    "commit 491e6346deeea505718f2cdf246647b70be2b5ab\n",
    "Author: Michele Mastropietro <michele.mastropietro@gmail.com>\n",
    "Date:   Sun Oct 9 23:36:16 2016 +0200\n",
    "\n",
    "    initial commit\n",
    "```"
   ]
